        {
            "title": "亞洲雄厚的外匯存底足以抵禦本幣貶值 多國央行已介入市場",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 隨著中東戰事升溫推高能源價格，亞洲各國央行握有的8萬億美元外匯存底，成為捍衛本幣的重要「火力」。對高度依賴石油進口的亞洲經濟體而言，油價飆升構成關鍵風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印尼、印度與台灣已介入市場，中國則透過上調每日人民幣中間價釋出穩匯訊號。其他國家當局目前多停留在口頭警告階段，同時密切關注市場波動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著投資人評估油價上漲對進口成本、通膨、經濟成長與財政收支的衝擊，亞洲貨幣普遍承壓。若匯率急貶，恐引發資本外流。本周，印度盧比跌至紀錄低點，韓元跌至全球金融危機以來的最低水平，印尼盾則跌至六周以來的最低點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4000fac9-0808-3c7f-94b5-8f4ff49b90ad-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Emkay Global Financial Services Ltd.首席經濟學家Madhavi Arora表示，匯率穩定是金融穩定的錨。當市場出現大量投機部位時，往往對宏觀經濟與市場產生超出基本面的負向回饋效應，因此各國央行必須嚴陣以待。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kn.2C503O9ZaxYiPKq3Q_g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a034de98c5fbec26b2181726e7d29009\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據彭博計算，亞洲主要央行的外匯存底自2024年底以來已增加約6,000億美元。過去一年，當局持續吸納資金流入，加上金價上漲與美元走弱，也推升了外匯存底的價值。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印尼央行高級副總裁Destry Damayanti周三表示，印尼正在干預外匯市場，將在離岸無本金交割遠期(NDF)、在岸NDF、現貨與債市持續「堅定且一致地」進場操作 。惠譽當天稍晚將印尼的信用評等展望下調至「負向」，理由是政策不確定性升高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">駐孟買的交易員表示，印度央行一直在賣出美元，此舉旨在支撐印度盧比，此前該貨幣已跌至紀錄低點。台灣央行外匯局局長蔡烱民周四在記者會上表示，本周在外資匯出金額比較大的時候，央行有進場調節。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Robust Asian Reserve Pile Positioned to Defend Currency Slide</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E9%9B%84%E5%8E%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AF%E5%AD%98%E5%BA%95%E8%B6%B3%E4%BB%A5%E6%8A%B5%E7%A6%A6%E6%9C%AC%E5%B9%A3%E8%B2%B6%E5%80%BC-%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%B7%B2%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-004125064.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-06 10:24:05",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "強勢美元壓制黃金 避險需求難敵跌勢 本週料將收低",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dAoDxJ0LT6Dj7XJl41UvJg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/gold_3_M_1440048042.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週五亞洲交易時段,黃金價格在前一交易日下跌後維持穩定,強勢美元和國債收益率上升的影響超過了中東衝突擴大帶來的避險需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貴金屬本週也將錄得大幅下跌,近期美元走強和降息預期減弱對金價構成壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間20:25(格林威治標準時間01:25),現貨黃金基本持平,報5,080.37美元/盎司。美國黃金期貨上漲0.3%,至5,091.040美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金在前一交易日下跌1%,本週料將下跌近4%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9c034389-b223-3111-bdcc-2df3a1df4411-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週五,中東衝突進入第七天,仍未見緩和跡象,令全球金融市場持續緊張。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">過去一週,美國、以色列與伊朗之間的戰鬥愈演愈烈,導彈襲擊和報復性攻擊在該地區蔓延,引發了對全球能源供應中斷的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統川普表示,他希望在戰爭結束後參與決定伊朗下一任領導人的人選,這番言論凸顯了該地區政治前景的高度不確定性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於衝突威脅到波斯灣關鍵能源基礎設施和航運路線,油價延續隔夜強勁漲勢。原油價格飆升引發了對新一輪全球通脹的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這使包括美國聯準會在內的全球央行前景變得複雜。油價上漲往往會推高通脹,可能使政策制定者在短期內對降息更加謹慎。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者現在將注意力轉向週五稍晚公佈的美國2月{{ecl-227||非農就業報告,該報告可能為勞動市場強度和貨幣政策方向提供新的信號。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">強於預期的數據可能會強化聯準會有空間推遲降息的觀點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金通常受益於地緣政治不確定性和較低利率,但本週由於美元走強和債券收益率上升降低了其吸引力,黃金難以獲得上漲動能。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其他貴金屬方面,白銀價格上漲0.5%至82.68美元/盎司,鉑金上漲0.7%至2,134.76美元/盎司。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%A2%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%A3%93%E5%88%B6%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91-%E9%81%BF%E9%9A%AA%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E9%9B%A3%E6%95%B5%E8%B7%8C%E5%8B%A2-%E6%9C%AC%E9%80%B1%E6%96%99%E5%B0%87%E6%94%B6%E4%BD%8E-023505080.html",
