            "title": "全球最大央行黃金買家 傳將大舉售金「護國」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"全球最大央行黃金買家 傳將大舉售金「護國」\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WCcmzs8A5LMJuUBL7R94hA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/4f3001a0-f678-11f0-bf7b-bf134945eb94\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">全球最大央行黃金買家 傳將大舉售金「護國」</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
